 Widersprüche und Potenziale für Veränderung zeigen sich in der pädagogischen Auseinandersetzung mit Differenz und Ungleichheit? Dabei diskutiert sie Intersektionalität als Analyse- und Reflexionsperspektive für Forschung und pädagogische Praxis in widersprüchlichen Verhältnissen.  aSocial relations of domination present teaching methods with a challenge, and confront it with the risk of reproducing them. In theoretical and empirical studies which use intersectionality to analyze conflicts and processes of othering as well as possibilities of change, Christine Riegel carves out the potential of intersectionality as a critical perspective for analysis and reflection for research and pedagogical practice: to what extent does othering occur in schools and youth work? In which ways is critical education work mired in this? And what potential for change do educators find in the critical confrontation with difference and inequality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aDifferenz. 4aDiskriminierung. 4aDominanz. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aIntersektionalität. 4aOthering. 4aPostcolonial Studies. 4aPädagogik. 4aPädagogisches Handeln. 4aSozialpädagogik. 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh  aDifference.  aDiscrimination.  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aHegemonic Power.  aIntersectionality.  aOthering.  aPedagogical Acting.  aPedagogy.  aPostcolonial Studies.  aSocial Pedagogy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070101208iTitle is part of eBook pac